    "Section III traces the evolution of Speech LLMs, covering the shift from cascaded pipelines to unified models and contrasting architectural paradigms based on discrete versus continuous speech modeling.",
    "Section IV examines the model structure of Speech LLMs, breaking it down into three stages: modality feature extraction, modality information fusion, and LLM inference.",
    "Section V reviews the training strategies of current Speech LLMs, while Section VI summarizes the key datasets used for pretraining and evaluation.",
    "Section VII discusses performance benchmarks and empirical results across various understanding tasks.",
    "Finally, Section VIII outlines open challenges and future directions for advancing deep speech understanding with LLMs."
